                        <p>CPU, RAM, storage, serial numbers, and model info collected from every device automatically.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature">
                        <h3>Software Inventory</h3>
                        <p>Every installed application on every device, with fleet-wide views showing device counts per app and version.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature">
